sequenceDiagram
    participant Developer as "Desenvolvedor"
    participant GitHub as "GitHub"
    participant GitHubActions as "GitHub Actions"
    participant CloudflarePages as "Cloudflare Pages"

    Developer->>GitHub: Push para main
    GitHub->>GitHubActions: Aciona workflows
    GitHubActions->>GitHubActions: Executa build e testes
    GitHubActions->>CloudflarePages: Deploy para Cloudflare Pages
    CloudflarePages->>CloudflarePages: Hospeda o jogo
